-- ============================================================================
-- TYPE COERCION FUNCTIONS
-- ============================================================================
-- These functions convert specific node types to the generic AudioNode type.
-- In JavaScript, all AudioNode subtypes are the same at runtime, so these
-- are identity functions. They provide type safety for Canopy's type system.

